## AI-assisted Development
- Validate AI-generated code before committing; review security implications.
- Test thoroughly, including edge cases; maintain project style consistency.
- Document complex AI-generated logic.
- Critical paths require human review.

## Automation Guidelines
- Automate repetitive tasks; version and document scripts.
- Robust error handling; logging; idempotency where possible.
